The paper proposes methods for decreasing the computational complexity of the sphere decoder used for ML detection of signals on the multi-antenna fading channel. This problem falls under the intersection of several CS sub-fields, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), systems and control (cs.SY), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
